<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Oct1933"><font color="red">8 October 1933</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from J. Ralph Pinker to Paul L&eacute;on): Have you &hellip; heard from the Servire Press &hellip; You will remember that the contract was held up until they had decided on the get-up of the edition. </div>
